{"name": "odoo14-addon-edi-voxel-oca", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-edi-voxel-oca", "version": "14.0.1.0.1.dev4", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://github.com/OCA/edi", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-base-iso3166", "odoo14-addon-product-supplierinfo-for-customer", "odoo14-addon-queue-job", "odoo14-addon-report-xml", "odoo"], "summary": "Base module for connecting with Voxel", "upload_time": 1705722429}, "documentation": ["---\nsubstitutions:\n  badge1: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/maturity-Beta-yellow.png\n    :alt: Beta\n    :target: https://odoo-community.org/page/development-status\n    ```\n  badge2: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.png\n    :alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n    :target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n    ```\n  badge3: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/github-OCA%2Fedi-lightgray.png?logo=github\n    :alt: OCA/edi\n    :target: https://github.com/OCA/edi/tree/14.0/edi_voxel_oca\n    ```\n  badge4: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/weblate-Translate%20me-F47D42.png\n    :alt: Translate me on Weblate\n    :target: https://translation.odoo-community.org/projects/edi-14-0/edi-14-0-edi_voxel_oca\n    ```\n  badge5: |-\n    ```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/runboat-Try%20me-875A7B.png\n    :alt: Try me on Runboat\n    :target: https://runboat.odoo-community.org/builds?repo=OCA/edi&target_branch=14.0\n    ```\n---\n\n# Voxel\n\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! This file is generated by oca-gen-addon-readme !!\n% !! changes will be overwritten.                   !!\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n% !! source digest: sha256:a05ef023cfa7e84a912dcd74ec75e6e9e2f3938ac930764eaa7c39d0c8d792e6\n% !!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\n\n{{ badge1 }} {{ badge2 }} {{ badge3 }} {{ badge4 }} {{ badge5 }}\n\nThis is a base module that allows you to send and receive documents\nsuch as Invoices, Sales Orders, Delivery Orders in XML format using\nthe baVel electronic platform belonging to Voxel Group.\n\nVoxel Group is a company that offers leading solutions for B2B payments,\neInvoicing, VAT refund and supply chain via its baVel Platform. For more\ninformation visit [https://www.voxelgroup.net/](https://www.voxelgroup.net/).\n\nThis module doesn't do anything useful by itself, but it is used by other modules:\n\n- *edi_voxel_account_invoice* to send invoices to Voxel.\n- *edi_voxel_stock_picking* to send delivery orders to Voxel.\n- *edi_voxel_sale_order_import* to import a sale order received from Voxel.\n\n**Table of contents**\n\n```{contents}\n:local: true\n```\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/OCA/edi/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us to smash it by providing a detailed and welcomed\n[feedback](https://github.com/OCA/edi/issues/new?body=module:%20edi_voxel_oca%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**).\n\nDo not contact contributors directly about support or help with technical issues.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Authors\n\n- Tecnativa\n\n### Contributors\n\n- [Tecnativa](https://www.tecnativa.com):\n\n  - Ernesto Tejeda\n  - Pedro M. Baeza\n\n### Maintainers\n\nThis module is maintained by the OCA.\n\n```{image} https://odoo-community.org/logo.png\n:alt: Odoo Community Association\n:target: https://odoo-community.org\n```\n\nOCA, or the Odoo Community Association, is a nonprofit organization whose\nmission is to support the collaborative development of Odoo features and\npromote its widespread use.\n\nThis module is part of the [OCA/edi](https://github.com/OCA/edi/tree/14.0/edi_voxel_oca) project on GitHub.\n\nYou are welcome to contribute. To learn how please visit <https://odoo-community.org/page/Contribute>.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models", "documentation": ["License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.account", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..account", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.queue_job", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..queue_job", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.res_company", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..res_company", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.res_config_settings", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..res_config_settings", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.res_partner", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..res_partner", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.uom_uom", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..uom_uom", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.voxel_login", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..voxel_login", "project": null}}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.voxel_mixin", "xref": {"fqname": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models..voxel_mixin", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.account", "documentation": ["Copyright 2019 Tecnativa - Ernesto Tejeda", "License AGPL-3.0 or later (http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl)."], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.account.AccountTax", "bases": ["models.Model"], "methods": [], "class_variables": [{"name": "odoo.addons.edi_voxel_oca.models.account.AccountTax._inherit", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "odoo.a